{"tid":1277936,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】被捕人士法律懶人包","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:45:56.000Z","uid":235080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ba416b88f09b1487e61cc30faa507e5572d3c8","tid":1277936,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"下面會解釋喺差館被扣留48個鐘嘅詳情<br />\n同埋提吓大家必須要留意嘅嘢<br />\n大家唔好俾狗有任何機會落charge<br />\n睇完幫手push 有咩唔明記住問<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>流程</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一般會<span style=\"color: green;\">扣你入臭格 隔一陣落口供</span> 折磨你<br />\n會用盡方法攞料 然後起訴 包括<span style=\"color: green;\">出陰招</span><br />\n你可以保釋 但要保釋金 同埋要定期報到<br />\n放棄嘅話 難捱 但48個鐘唔起訴就放人<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: green;\">唔洗unlock電話</span> 同埋<span style=\"color: green;\">可以去醫院驗傷</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>臭格</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n臭格嘅真名叫<span style=\"color: green;\">羈留室</span> 一般每間差館都有<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">同坐監好似</span> 三面牆 石屎床 踎廁 每日三餐<br />\n唔同嘅係<span style=\"color: green;\">你可以叫外賣 或者屋企人送嘢食</span><br />\n你可以要求鵝肝 但唔可以要魚 因為有骨<br />\n俗語叫臭格係因為狗可以唔幫你沖廁<br />\n沖廁只可以佢搞 搞到好撚臭 <span style=\"color: green;\">環境極惡劣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>口供</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">口供有兩份</span> 一份個人背景 一份事發案情<br />\n記住 <span style=\"color: green;\">名同地址可以講 其他咩都唔好講</span><br />\n佢問你任何嘢 你都係答佢四隻字 <span style=\"color: green;\">我冇嘢講</span><br />\n沉默係你嘅權利 唔係阻差辦公 唔係犯法<br />\n佢會燥底 但吹你唔漲 <span style=\"color: green;\">無謂同畜生溝通</span><br />\n<br />\n要同自己講<span style=\"color: green;\">要淡定</span> 啲老屎忽有番咁上下<br />\n成日一開頭問個人資料嚟撬開你把口<br />\n或且兩隻狗 一隻醜人一隻好人 令到你亂<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">唔好覺得有啲警察好</span> 唔好有惻隱之心<br />\n密切<span style=\"color: green;\">留意自己心情</span> 保持平靜 '<span style=\"color: green;\">我冇嘢講</span>'<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">落完口供睇清楚</span> 啲狗唔覺意會寫多咗<br />\ncheck完再check再check再check<br />\n但都<span style=\"color: green;\">唔好簽</span> 因為冇一份文件你一定要簽<br />\n不過記住<span style=\"color: green;\">要求攞副本</span> 留做reference<br />\n口供係班狗鋤你嘅最好證據 萬分小心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>律師</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n48個鐘入面 要<span style=\"color: green;\">不斷要求打俾律師</span> 好重要<br />\n最好自己記咗啲電話 佢未必會俾本嘢你<br />\n基本上<span style=\"color: green;\">邊個都得</span> 保釋好多人做 個個都識做<br />\n同埋<span style=\"color: green;\">唔洗驚唔識個律師</span> 佢會先了解你情況<br />\n記住 <span style=\"color: green;\">用警署電話打</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">唔好俾機會狗搶電話</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>陰招</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- 落口供嗰時你可以解釋自己㗎<br />\n- 你認咗佢 我早啲放你走 / 可以減刑<br />\n- 有齊曬料告你 你好快啲認咗佢<br />\n- 同你吹水 (條例真係咁差? 政府會點樣?)<br />\n- 鋤到你好撚眼訓 (記住要保持清醒)<br />\n- 扮打電話俾你 你unlock去睇時就獵走咗<br />\n- 較凍冷氣 / 遲俾飯食 / 遲俾你去廁所"},{"pid":"6c551cddb3dc49daccd0c48f0d5f5ab01259f89f","tid":1277936,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829ab27c9f20df71a3bb54ac85de957b7576bbbe","tid":1277936,"uid":92273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"790ee6cec5a32636687f91befa07d2a90c152e6d","tid":1277936,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cce13ee7367fb667bec184a2d23fd7bb6299af","tid":1277936,"uid":20711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4eb6892f8d730783b9f785697df6ad7025de62b","tid":1277936,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\